#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn1.74"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn1.74:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 1 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 1 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.74:0.2"
msgid "8. Chetvāvagga "
msgstr "8. Incinerated "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn1.74:0.3"
msgid "74. Vuṭṭhisutta "
msgstr "74. Rain "

#. HTML: </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.95, sc1
msgctxt "sn1.74:1.1"
msgid "“Kiṃsu uppatataṃ seṭṭhaṃ, "
msgstr "“What’s the best of things that rise? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.74:1.2"
msgid "kiṃsu nipatataṃ varaṃ; "
msgstr "And what’s the finest of things that fall? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.74:1.3"
msgid "Kiṃsu pavajamānānaṃ, "
msgstr "And what of the things that go forth? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.74:1.4"
msgid "kiṃsu pavadataṃ varan”ti. "
msgstr "And who’s the finest speaker?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn1.74:2.1"
msgid "“Bījaṃ uppatataṃ seṭṭhaṃ, "
msgstr "“A seed’s the best of things that rise. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.74:2.2"
msgid "vuṭṭhi nipatataṃ varā; "
msgstr "Rain’s the finest thing that falls. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.74:2.3"
msgid "Gāvo pavajamānānaṃ, "
msgstr "Cattle, of things that go forth. "

# NOTE: BB explains that the comm thinks this means a son won’t testify against you in a court of law. Maybe! If this was so, translating as son would be appropriate. But i think it refers to the joy a parent feels when they hear their child speak for the first time, and there no gender matters.
#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.74:2.4"
msgid "putto pavadataṃ varo”ti. "
msgstr "And a child is the finest speaker.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn1.74:3.1"
msgid "“Vijjā uppatataṃ seṭṭhā, "
msgstr "“Knowledge is best of things that rise. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.74:3.2"
msgid "avijjā nipatataṃ varā; "
msgstr "Ignorance the finest thing that falls. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.74:3.3"
msgid "Saṅgho pavajamānānaṃ, "
msgstr "The Saṅgha, of things that go forth. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.74:3.4"
msgid "buddho pavadataṃ varo”ti. "
msgstr "And the Buddha is the finest speaker.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
